{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866141208,"sessionID":"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy","part":{"id":"prt_d79de7232001NofOtWli6Ss2io","messageID":"msg_d79de5a58001pRE28xu7Jl8Yhe","sessionID":"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_0cbe56ce7b874d74bd7debaa","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model Enhancements\n\n- [ ] **T001** Review existing `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verify all fields from design are present\n  - Confirm validators: `validate_language`, `validate_build_mode`, `validate_port`\n\n- [ ] **T002** Write unit tests for `AgentMetadata` validators:\n  - Test invalid language value raises ValidationError\n  - Test invalid build_mode value raises ValidationError\n  - Test port out of range (1-65535) raises ValidationError\n  - Test language normalization (uppercase to lowercase)\n\n- [ ] **T003** Run existing tests to verify current implementation:\n  - `pytest tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: MetadataService Load Operations\n\n- [ ] **T010** Verify existing `load_metadata` fallback chain:\n  - `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\n  - `agent.yaml` (fallback)\n  - `metadata.yaml` (fallback)\n\n- [ ] **T011** Verify error handling:\n  - Test `FileNotFoundError` when no metadata file exists\n\n- [ ] **T012** Run existing load tests to confirm functionality\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: MetadataService Save Operations\n\n- [ ] **T020** Update `save_metadata` to match YAML formatting requirements:\n  - Add `indent=2` parameter to `yaml.safe_dump`\n  - Add `exclude_none=True` to `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\n\n- [ ] **T021** Write test for YAML formatting:\n  - Verify output uses `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`\n  - Verify `None` fields are excluded\n\n- [ ] **T022** Run save tests to verify formatting\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: MetadataService Update Operations\n\n- [ ] **T030** Implement `update_metadata` method in `MetadataService`:\n  ```python\n  @staticmethod\n  def update_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n      \"\"\"Update existing metadata with new values and re-validate.\"\"\"\n  ```\n\n- [ ] **T031** Implement partial field update logic:\n  - Load existing metadata\n  - Merge updates into existing metadata\n  - Re-validate the updated model\n  - Save the updated metadata\n\n- [ ] **T032** Write unit tests for `update_metadata`:\n  - Test partial field update preserves existing fields\n  - Test update triggers re-validation (invalid values raise ValidationError)\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: Workspace Validation\n\n- [ ] **T040** Implement `_validate_python_workspace` method:\n  - Check for `*.py` files in workspace\n  - Raise `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")` if none found\n\n- [ ] **T041** Implement `_validate_java_workspace` method:\n  - Check for `pom.xml` in workspace\n  - Raise `ValueError(\"No pom.xml found in workspace\")` if not found\n\n- [ ] **T042** Implement public `validate_workspace` method that delegates to language-specific validators:\n  - Takes `workspace_path` and `metadata: AgentMetadata` as parameters\n\n- [ ] **T043** Write unit tests for workspace validation:\n  - Test valid Python workspace passes\n  - Test Python workspace missing .py files raises error\n  - Test valid Java workspace passes\n  - Test Java workspace missing pom.xml raises error\n\n---\n\n### Phase 6: MetadataOptions from CLI Options\n\n- [ ] **T050** Review existing `MetadataOptions` dataclass in `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n\n- [ ] **T051** Implement `from_options` class method:\n  ```python\n  @classmethod\n  def from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> MetadataOptions:\n      \"\"\"Convert CLI options dict to MetadataOptions with defaults.\"\"\"\n  ```\n\n- [ ] **T052** Handle defaults:\n  - `language='python'`\n  - `port=8080`\n  - `build_mode='local'`\n  - Empty strings for Optional fields (`router_url`, `workload_manager_url`, etc.)\n\n- [ ] **T053** Write unit tests for `MetadataOptions.from_options`:\n  - Test full options conversion\n  - Test partial options with defaults\n  - Test empty strings treated as default values\n\n---\n\n### Phase 7: Integration with Runtimes\n\n- [ ] **T060** Review existing runtime files:\n  - `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`\n\n- [ ] **T061** Verify build metadata integration:\n  - Confirm `_update_build_metadata` method exists or needs implementation\n  - Store `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n\n- [ ] **T062** Verify publish metadata integration:\n  - Confirm `_update_publish_metadata` method exists or needs implementation\n  - Store `session_id` after AgentRuntime CR deployment\n  - Store `agent_id` for status checks\n\n- [ ] **T063** Verify K8s deployment info storage:\n  - Store `k8s_deployment` with `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `replicas`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 8: Provider Integration\n\n- [ ] **T070** Review `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`:\n  - Verify `workload_manager_url` and `router_url` are passed as env vars\n\n- [ ] **T071** Review `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`:\n  - Verify `agent_name`, `port`, `entrypoint` are used in Deployment container config\n\n- [ ] **T072** Implement `_get_cr_k8s_status` if needed:\n  - Extract `agentEndpoint` from CR status\n\n---\n\n### Phase 9: End-to-End Testing\n\n- [ ] **T080** Run full test suite:\n  - `pytest tests/ -v`\n\n- [ ] **T081** Test pack command end-to-end:\n  - Create test workspace with Python files\n  - Run pack command\n  - Verify metadata saved correctly\n\n- [ ] **T082** Test metadata validation end-to-end:\n  - Create metadata with invalid language\n  - Verify ValidationError is raised\n\n---\n\n### Phase 10: Build & Verify\n\n- [ ] **T090** Run Python linter:\n  - `ruff check agentcube/`\n\n- [ ] **T091** Run type checker (if configured):\n  - `mypy agentcube/`\n\n- [ ] **T092** Verify all tests pass:\n  - `pytest tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T001 | None |\n| T002 | T001 |\n| T003 | T002 |\n| T010 | T001 |\n| T011 | T010 |\n| T012 | T011 |\n| T020 | T001 |\n| T021 | T020 |\n| T022 | T021 |\n| T030 | T012, T022 |\n| T031 | T030 |\n| T032 | T031 |\n| T040 | None |\n| T041 | None |\n| T042 | T040, T041 |\n| T043 | T042 |\n| T050 | None |\n| T051 | T050 |\n| T052 | T051 |\n| T053 | T052 |\n| T060 | All above |\n| T061 | T060 |\n| T062 | T060 |\n| T063 | T060 |\n| T070 | T061 |\n| T071 | T060 |\n| T072 | T071 |\n| T080 | All implementation |\n| T081 | T080 |\n| T082 | T080 |\n| T090 | All implementation |\n| T091 | T090 |\n| T092 | T091 |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md`\n- Design: `cli-toolkit/design.md`\n- Base Spec: `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n- Existing Model: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- Existing Models: `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n- Existing Tests: `tests/test_metadata_service.py`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tests/test_metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/models/pack_models.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-c